card_text: This card's name becomes "Shiranui Style Synthesis" while in the Spell & Trap Zone. Once per turn, you can activate 1 of these effects.$N●Banish 1 Zombie monster from your GY; the Normal and Special Summons of your Zombie monsters cannot be negated for the rest of this turn (even if this card leaves the field).$N●Target 1 Zombie monster you control; banish it, then you can send 1 Zombie monster with 0 DEF from your Deck to the GY.
